Marc Bell (entrepreneur)

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






A major contributor to this article appears to have a close connection with its subject. It may require cleanup to comply with Wikipedia's content policies, particularly neutral point of view. Please discuss further on the talk page. (February 2015) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)




Marc H. Bell





Born
Brooklyn, New York, US


Residence
Boca Raton, Florida, US


