Insider Activity


Individual




Marc H. Bell



Mr. Marc H. Bell is a Managing Director at Marc Bell Capital Partners LLC and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at FastCupid, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at JAVELIN Mortgage Investment Corp., ARMOUR Residential REIT, Inc., New York University, FastCupid, Inc., and New York University School of Medicine.
Mr. Bell was previously employed as Chairman & Treasurer by Enterprise Acquisition Corp., Executive Co-Chairman & Chief Strategy Officer by FriendFinder Networks, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Penthouse Media Group, Inc., Chairman by NEON Communications Group, Inc., Chairman & President by Globix Corp., and Founder by Naft International Ltd. He also served on the board at EDGAR Online, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Babson College and a graduate degree from New York University.



